# Browserslist configuration for modern browsers
# This reduces JavaScript bundle size by eliminating unnecessary polyfills

# Target only modern browsers that support ES2020+ features natively
Chrome >= 90
Firefox >= 88
Safari >= 14
Edge >= 90
iOS >= 14
Android >= 8

# Exclude all old browsers that require polyfills
not IE 11
not IE_Mob 11
not Chrome < 90
not Firefox < 88
not Safari < 14
not Edge < 90
not iOS < 14
not Android < 8
not dead
not op_mini all
